            "source": "curl --request GET \\\n  --url 'https://sandboxapi.deere.com/platform/partnerships/abc123-partnership-token/permissions' \\\n  --header 'Authorization: Bearer <access_token>' \\\n  --header 'Accept: application/vnd.deere.axiom.v3+json'"
          }
        ],
